 74Ôćĺ * for the given webview label. This is emitted by Electron's `did-finish-load`
 75Ôćĺ * callback ÔÇö no polling needed.
 76Ôćĺ *
 77Ôćĺ * When `alsoListenUrlChange` is true (for history.back() in SPAs), also
 78Ôćĺ * resolves on `browser:url-change` since SPA routers don't trigger a
 79Ôćĺ * real page load ÔÇö they fire popstate which emits url-change instead.
 80Ôćĺ *
